meanings: 실용회화-예약 안했을 때 Do you have a table for three?

vlive.korean: 기사님 세 명이요 - 아가씨 혼자 타면서 왜 세 명이야? There are 3 of us, driver. - Why do you say 3, when you're the only one? 듣기 View video Dispatch : [ⓓxV] “아기천사즈 칭찬 대파티” (한결, 도현 : H&D)
vlive.english: There are 3 of us, driver. - Why do you say 3, when you're the only one?

vlive.korean: 여기 잘생긴 사람 몇 명이야? - 세 명이요 - 세 명이 누군데? How many? - Three. - Who are they? 듣기 View video Stray Kids : First UNLOCK in Chicago❤
vlive.english: How many? - Three. - Who are they?

vlive.korean: 하나 더 시켰어요 근데 "세 명이서" - 다섯... - "다섯 개요?" So we ordered one more. And the waitress said "5 dishes for 3"? 듣기 View video NCT : 127💚니가좋아💚
vlive.english: So we ordered one more. And the waitress said "5 dishes for 3"?

vlive.korean: 저희는 이제 두 명이서 치면 바로바로 이렇게 할 수 있는데 세 명이서 치면... It's easier when there's only two. But if there's three... 듣기 View video WOODZ (조승연) : (진짜)조곤조곤
vlive.english: It's easier when there's only two. But if there's three...

vlive.korean: 6인분에 양밥 - 세 명이서 6인분이면 많이 먹은 거 아니야? 6 servings and fried rice. - If three of you had 6 servings, isn't that a lot? 듣기 View video Stray Kids : We love Felix and Phoenix❤
vlive.english: 6 servings and fried rice. - If three of you had 6 servings, isn't that a lot?
